हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Lily Ghosh, an undercover journalist posing as a social media manager who infiltrates the royal Raj Mahal to expose Prince Aryan's alleged scandals. Initially sent by vengeful ex-employee Mukul to destroy Aryan's reputation, Lily finds herself drawn into a complex web of palace intrigue involving the mysterious return of Aryan's supposedly dead brother Rishan after 15 years. As Lily navigates between her journalistic mission and growing feelings for Aryan, she uncovers shocking secrets: Rishan is actually the illegitimate son of King Abhay Singh and a palace manager, Queen Rajeshwari's death wasn't accidental, and Rishan has returned with murderous intentions to claim the throne. The story culminates in dramatic revelations at Rishan's coronation ceremony where Lily exposes his attempted patricide and illegitimate status, leading to a violent confrontation where Aryan shoots Rishan to save Lily, ultimately resulting in their romantic union.
